&lt;p&gt;You will operate at the intersection of sales, media strategy, and technical solutioning. This role is designed for a commercially driven seller who can translate platform capabilities into clear business outcomes, influence agency planning, and close deals across multiple channels and formats.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will own a book of business and be responsible for driving revenue through agency relationships and new opportunities. This includes educating partners on the MrBeast and Vyro ecosystem, shaping integrated media strategies, and closing deals that combine social amplification with premium ad inventory.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will operate across the full sales cycle, from initial outreach and solution design through execution alignment and renewal, while partnering closely with internal teams to ensure delivery matches client expectations.&lt;/p&gt;
