&lt;li&gt;Develop and manage relationships with agency account, strategy, and planning teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Position Vyro and MrBeast media offerings within larger agency media plans and campaign concepts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design multi-platform solutions that combine creator integrations, social amplification, and paid media&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate platform capabilities into clear, outcome-driven proposals for clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sell advertising inventory across YouTube channels, FAST, and CTV partnerships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the full sales cycle from agency education through deal execution and renewal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal teams to align campaign design with production and delivery capabilities&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support post-campaign analysis and use performance data to drive renewals and upsell opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
