&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Responsible for project organization which includes: ingesting, synching, logging, string outs and selects&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Responsible for deliverables, renderings and other tasks provided by the editor&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
