&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Knowledgeable of social media and digital video platforms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Great communication skills to ensure smooth project operations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Detail-oriented, technical, and open to new ideas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Comfortable working with most video codecs, formats, timecode formats, and transcoding if needed&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Flexibility to adapt with changing timelines and deliverables&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
