&lt;p data-start=&quot;152&quot; data-end=&quot;498&quot;&gt;The Main Channel Brand Creative is embedded within the content team and is responsible for developing and executing brand partnership creative specifically for main channel videos. This role translates brand briefs into concepts that meet partner objectives while preserving the tone, quality, and audience-first approach of main channel content.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;500&quot; data-end=&quot;734&quot;&gt;This role is fully dedicated to brand integrations on main channel. It does not support non-brand content. Success is defined by ensuring brand partnerships are creatively strong, aligned with content standards, and delivered on time.&lt;/p&gt;
