&lt;p data-start=&quot;751&quot; data-end=&quot;1067&quot;&gt;You will own the creative development of brand integrations for main channel content from brief through pitch and execution alignment. This includes shaping how brands are integrated into videos, ensuring concepts meet both partner goals and content expectations, and maintaining consistency across partnership arcs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1069&quot; data-end=&quot;1234&quot;&gt;You act as the creative authority for brand presence on main channel. You are responsible for protecting content quality while enabling effective brand partnerships.&lt;/p&gt;
