&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;djjh2d&quot; data-start=&quot;1578&quot; data-end=&quot;1691&quot;&gt;Partner with business development and partnerships teams to create pitch-ready concepts for prospective deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;vueq3u&quot; data-start=&quot;1692&quot; data-end=&quot;1791&quot;&gt;Build visual mockups, narrative walkthroughs, and campaign story arcs for partner presentations&lt;/l

