&lt;p&gt;Beast Industries is a multifaceted media and entertainment company founded by Jimmy Donaldson, popularly known as MrBeast, the most watched person in the world. Renowned for revolutionizing digital content creation, Beast Industries encompasses a diverse portfolio of ventures that extend far beyond its origins on YouTube. With a mission to entertain, inspire, and create significant social impact, Beast Industries operates across various domains including digital media, philanthropy, consumer products, and innovative business initiatives. At Beast Industries, we believe in the transformative power of digital media and its potential to entertain, educate, and effect positive change. Our commitment to innovation, creativity, and philanthropy drives us to explore new frontiers, create unforgettable experiences, and build a legacy that inspires future generations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Data Science Lead Engineering Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Primary: Bay Area (San Francisco / Peninsula) &amp;nbsp; | &amp;nbsp; Secondary: NYC&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re doing an AI-first engineering rebuild for a company that already has an audience of 100M+ people. This is a zero-to-one build with no legacy constraints. You&#39;re here to build a data foundation: establishing AI-facilitated analysis processes and tooling that unlock super-fast feature iteration. Alongside that, you&#39;ll architect the large-scale data pipeline that supports real-time telemetry, long-term metric monitoring, and A/B experimentation at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Product&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be the senior technical anchor for data science, owning the full journey from business question to data analysis to product insight that drives decisions. The work spans consumer products, media, game, and e-commerce analytics, all sitting on top of a large and fast-growing user base. That means:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build the data analysis mechanisms that turn raw user behavior into actionable product insights, powering decisions on what to build, what to fix, and where the biggest opportunities are.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Architect and own the data platform end to end: the full tech stack covering data collection, processing, and visualization that makes reliable, real-time analytics possible at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage AI to accelerate the productivity of the data science team, embedding AI-facilitated tooling and workflows that enable faster product iteration and shorter feedback loops.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set and enforce the data standards for product launches: validation, reproducibility, experimentation, and monitoring frameworks that every team relies on before and after shipping.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the A/B experimentation framework end to end, from experiment design and statistical rigor through to result interpretation and product decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the engineering and operation of the data pipeline, ensuring the right data freshness, coverage, and observability to support product and business decisions at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guide the technical work of data scientists and engineers through design review, pairing, and mentorship, growing the team&#39;s capabilities alongside the product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-Native: &lt;/strong&gt;You&#39;re already burning through tokens and using AI tools daily to accelerate your data science workflow, from analysis to insight to decision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Science Builder: &lt;/strong&gt;8+ years designing, building, and operating data science syste

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beast Industries is a multifaceted media and entertainment company founded by Jimmy Donaldson, popularly known as MrBeast, the most watched person in the world. Renowned for revolutionizing digital content creation, Beast Industries encompasses a diverse portfolio of ventures that extend far beyond its origins on YouTube. With a mission to entertain, inspire, and create significant social impact, Beast Industries operates across various domains including digital media, philanthropy, consumer products, and innovative business initiatives. At Beast Industries, we believe in the transformative power of digital media and its potential to entertain, educate, and effect positive change. Our commitment to innovation, creativity, and philanthropy drives us to explore new frontiers, create unforgettable experiences, and build a legacy that inspires future generations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Science Lead, Global Creator Platform&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beast Industries is building the operating system for creator monetization — the connective tissue between the world&#39;s biggest creators and the brands that want to reach their audiences. Vyro is our brand-creator marketplace, and we believe there&#39;s a real opportunity to do something here that no one else in the space is set up to do.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Where&#39;s the real incrementality — and how much is it worth?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring a Data Science Lead, reporting to the CTO, to design and run the experiments that will help us answer it. You’ll start as a senior individual contributor and help build a quant team over time. You&#39;ll build a portfolio of incrementality tests, lift studies, measurement frameworks, and whatever else helps drive the platform forwards. You should expect many of our strongest beliefs about creator marketing to be wrong - a key part of this role is designing experiments that overturn assumptions and help us discover what actually drives outcomes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an early role on a new team still finding its shape. You&#39;ll work directly with leadership, sit close to the engineers and product people building Vyro, and have a direct line to the creative talent that powers Beast. You&#39;ll be one of the people figuring this out from scratch, alongside the team behind the most-watched creator on the planet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help us run our first real campaigns and learn from them — fast. Design tests that get useful answers in weeks and tighten the methodology with each iteration.&lt;/li&gt;
