&lt;li&gt;Identify cultural, industry, and consumer trends that create opportunities for brand storytelling and thought leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead proactive and reactive communications planning, including issues management and crisis communications support when needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cultivate and maintain senior-level relationships with top-tier journalists, editors, producers, podcast hosts, creators, and industry influencers&lt;/li&gt;
