&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with retention specialists and creative leads to optimize content pacing and viewer engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working alongside other editors to share techniques, improve workflows, and maintain consistent quality&lt;/li&gt;
