&lt;li&gt;Strong experience with motion graphics, rotoscoping, and basic compositing techniques&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to craft edits for YouTube-style content (fast-paced, high-retention, cinematic when needed)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly accountable and reliable, consistently hitting or exceeding deadlines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open to feedback, and able to incorporate notes quickly and effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for storytelling, creativity, and experimenting with new techniques&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A demo reel that showcases editing speed, motion graphics, and stylistic variety (applications without reels may not be considered)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
